{"slug": "api/angular", "content_type": "text/html", "name": "api_angular", "head": {}, "html": {"main": "<section id=\"page-header\" class=\"page-header-outer api_angular-header\">\n    <div class=\"layer\">\n        <div class=\"page-header\">\n            <div class=\"container fullpage\">\n                <div class=\"row fullpage\">\n                    <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\n                        <breadcrumbs></breadcrumbs>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<div id=\"page-main\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"api_angular-main col-md-12\">\n                <div class=\"center-block\" style=\"max-width: 900px\" data-highlight data-hash-scroll>\n                    <div class=\"section\" id=\"module-lux.extensions.angular\">\n<span id=\"angularjs-integration\"></span><span id=\"extension-angular\"></span><h1>AngularJS Integration<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#module-lux.extensions.angular\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<p>THis extension does not provide any middleware but it is required\nwhen using <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../js/#jsapi\"><em>lux.js</em></a> javascript module and\nprovides the link between <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://angularjs.org/\">AngularJS</a> and Python.</p>\n<p><strong>Required extensions</strong>: <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"ui#module-lux.extensions.ui\" title=\"lux.extensions.ui\"><tt class=\"xref py py-mod docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">lux.extensions.ui</span></tt></a></p>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"usage\">\n<h2>Usage<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#usage\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<p>Include <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">lux.extensions.angular</span></tt> into the <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"params#std:setting-EXTENSIONS\"><tt class=\"xref std std-setting docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">EXTENSIONS</span></tt></a> list in your\n<a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"params#parameters\"><em>config file</em></a>:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-python\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre>EXTENSIONS = [\n    ...\n    &#39;lux.extensions.ui&#39;,\n    &#39;lux.extensions.angular&#39;\n    ...\n    ]\n\n ANGULAR_UI_ROUTER = True\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n<p>There are two different ways to serve html. The default way is to serve without\nthe use of angular <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/angular-ui/ui-router\">ui-router</a>, in which case urls load the whole html5\ndocument each time they are accessed.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"ui-router\">\n<span id=\"spa-router\"></span><h2>UI-Router<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#ui-router\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<p>When switching <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"params#std:setting-ANGULAR_UI_ROUTER\"><tt class=\"xref std std-setting docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">ANGULAR_UI_ROUTER</span></tt></a> to <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">True</span></tt>, each page served by\nan angular <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router\" title=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router\"><tt class=\"xref py py-class docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">Router</span></tt></a> is managed, in javascript, by the <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/angular-ui/ui-router\">ui-router</a> as\na single page application.</p>\n<dl class=\"class\">\n<dt id=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router\">\n<em class=\"property\">class </em><tt class=\"descclassname\">lux.extensions.angular.</tt><tt class=\"descname\">Router</tt><big>(</big><em>*args</em>, <em>**kwargs</em><big>)</big><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../modules/lux/extensions/angular#Router\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\">[source]</span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>A <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router\" title=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router\"><tt class=\"xref py py-class docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">Router</span></tt></a> for Angular navigation.</p>\n<dl class=\"attribute\">\n<dt id=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router.html_body_template\">\n<tt class=\"descname\">html_body_template</tt><em class=\"property\"> = None</em><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router.html_body_template\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>The template for the body part of the Html5 document. In most cases it\nis as simple as:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-python\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre>$html_main\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n<p>where the <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">$html_main</span></tt> is replaced by the string created by the\n<a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router.build_main\" title=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router.build_main\"><tt class=\"xref py py-meth docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">build_main()</span></tt></a> method.</p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"attribute\">\n<dt id=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router.ngmodules\">\n<tt class=\"descname\">ngmodules</tt><em class=\"property\"> = None</em><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router.ngmodules\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Optional list of angular modules to include</p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"attribute\">\n<dt id=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router.uirouter\">\n<tt class=\"descname\">uirouter</tt><em class=\"property\"> = True</em><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router.uirouter\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Override the <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"params#std:setting-ANGULAR_UI_ROUTER\"><tt class=\"xref std std-setting docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">ANGULAR_UI_ROUTER</span></tt></a> setting for this\n<a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router\" title=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router\"><tt class=\"xref py py-class docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">Router</span></tt></a>. If set to <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">False</span></tt> the <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/angular-ui/ui-router\">ui-router</a> won&#8217;t be used\nand the whole html5 document is loaded when accessed.</p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"method\">\n<dt id=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router.get\">\n<tt class=\"descname\">get</tt><big>(</big><em>request</em><big>)</big><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../modules/lux/extensions/angular#Router.get\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\">[source]</span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router.get\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>This is the only http method implemented.</p>\n<p>If this <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router\" title=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router\"><tt class=\"xref py py-class docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">Router</span></tt></a> is operating in <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#spa-router\"><em>ui mode</em></a>,\nthis method performs the following tasks:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p class=\"first\">Collets children routers operating in <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#spa-router\"><em>ui mode</em></a>\nand build the sitemap used by angular <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/angular-ui/ui-router\">ui-router</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"first\">The <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">$html_main</span></tt> content, rendered by the <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router.build_main\" title=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router.build_main\"><tt class=\"xref py py-meth docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">build_main()</span></tt></a> method is\nwrapped by a <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">div</span></tt> element:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-python\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre>&lt;div id=&quot;seo-view&quot; data-ui-main=&quot;main&quot; class=&quot;hidden&quot;&gt;\n    $html_main\n&lt;/div&gt;\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"method\">\n<dt id=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router.build_main\">\n<tt class=\"descname\">build_main</tt><big>(</big><em>request</em><big>)</big><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../modules/lux/extensions/angular#Router.build_main\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\">[source]</span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router.build_main\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Build the main view for this router</p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"method\">\n<dt id=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router.uiview\">\n<tt class=\"descname\">uiview</tt><big>(</big><em>app</em>, <em>main</em>, <em>jscontext</em><big>)</big><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../modules/lux/extensions/angular#Router.uiview\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\">[source]</span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router.uiview\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Wrap the <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">main</span></tt> html with a <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">ui-view</span></tt> container.\nAdd animation class if specified in <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"params#std:setting-ANGULAR_VIEW_ANIMATE\"><tt class=\"xref std std-setting docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">ANGULAR_VIEW_ANIMATE</span></tt></a>.</p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"method\">\n<dt id=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router.state_template\">\n<tt class=\"descname\">state_template</tt><big>(</big><em>app</em><big>)</big><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../modules/lux/extensions/angular#Router.state_template\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\">[source]</span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router.state_template\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Template for ui-router state associated with this router.</p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"method\">\n<dt id=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router.angular_page\">\n<tt class=\"descname\">angular_page</tt><big>(</big><em>app</em>, <em>page</em><big>)</big><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../modules/lux/extensions/angular#Router.angular_page\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\">[source]</span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router.angular_page\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Callback for adding additional data to angular page object</p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"method\">\n<dt id=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router.sitemap\">\n<tt class=\"descname\">sitemap</tt><big>(</big><em>app</em>, <em>ngmodules</em><big>)</big><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../modules/lux/extensions/angular#Router.sitemap\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\">[source]</span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router.sitemap\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Build the sitemap used by angular <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/angular-ui/ui-router\">ui-router</a></p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"method\">\n<dt id=\"lux.extensions.angular.Router.instance_url\">\n<tt class=\"descname\">instance_url</tt><big>(</big><em>request</em>, <em>instance</em><big>)</big><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../modules/lux/extensions/angular#Router.instance_url\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\">[source]</span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#lux.extensions.angular.Router.instance_url\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Return the url for editing the <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">instance</span></tt></p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n</dd></dl>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<d